WEBVTT

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.159
The Treason Case of Censor Chao Heng

00:01:42.959 --> 00:01:44.280
The Treason Case of Censor Chao Heng

00:02:03.239 --> 00:02:03.920
Ye Li

00:02:05.159 --> 00:02:05.840
What is it?

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:07.359
Come with me.

00:02:27.479 --> 00:02:28.039
Ledgers.

00:02:30.599 --> 00:02:32.439
Every transaction of the All-Knowing Manor...

00:02:32.840 --> 00:02:34.080
...is recorded right here.

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:37.319
Human trafficking, selling offices...

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:40.479
...smuggling salt and wine.

00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:43.400
Every capital crime in the law...

00:02:44.240 --> 00:02:45.439
...can be found in here.

00:02:47.039 --> 00:02:47.800
Tell me...

00:02:48.479 --> 00:02:50.879
...did the Manor Lord build this huge storeroom...

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:52.840
...just to store these proofs of guilt?

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:55.479
Because only by keeping evidence...

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:59.159
...can one control officials and sway the court.

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.479
Why is there an Empress's Edict here?

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:11.919
If the All-Knowing Manor's backer is the Empress Dowager...

00:03:13.199 --> 00:03:15.759
...this shouldn't be here.

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:18.039
Unless...

00:03:18.039 --> 00:03:18.879
Unless...

00:03:19.639 --> 00:03:20.879
...it was Lord Nine Thousand Years...

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:22.879
...who forged the Empress's Edict.

00:03:24.479 --> 00:03:25.560
Aren't they on the same side?

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:28.080
I'm afraid our Lord Nine Thousand Years...

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.039
...has far greater ambitions.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.520
If the Empress Dowager knew...

00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:34.360
...the secrets hidden in the All-Knowing Manor...

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:38.000
...she'd likely skin that old eunuch alive.

00:03:38.719 --> 00:03:39.520
By the way, Master Kun...

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:41.039
...you need to think of a way quickly...

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:42.680
...to notify the Dali Temple.

00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:44.840
Get them to raid the manor.

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:46.759
Don't rush.

00:03:47.199 --> 00:03:47.919
Look at this.

00:03:55.759 --> 00:03:56.560
The Metropolitan Governor.

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:01.319
Look here.

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:04.800
"On the 23rd, Lord Meng is off duty. Act that night."

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:07.840
"Send experts from the manor. Leave no loose ends."

00:04:09.479 --> 00:04:10.680
The 23rd of last month...

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:13.599
...was the day Lord Meng summoned me to his residence.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:17.199
It was also the day Lord Meng was murdered.

00:04:17.480 --> 00:04:18.120
That's right.

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:20.360
The letter only mentioned assassination...

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:22.560
...it didn't say anything about finding a scapegoat.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:26.720
And you were summoned on short notice.

00:04:27.759 --> 00:04:28.959
Why were you implicated?

00:04:31.519 --> 00:04:32.399
Speaking of that...

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:34.360
...that is another tale of injustice.

00:05:19.439 --> 00:05:21.079
The petals disappeared at the inner chamber.

00:05:21.319 --> 00:05:22.279
The person is gone too.

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:23.920
Look for a mechanism.

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.279
If you can't find one...

00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:29.040
...tear this place apart for me.

00:05:29.439 --> 00:05:29.759
Yes, sir.

00:05:30.439 --> 00:05:30.959
Search the place!

00:05:44.959 --> 00:05:45.800
Rest assured.

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:48.240
No matter what happens with the manor case...

00:05:49.319 --> 00:05:52.079
...I will do my best regarding the Chao family's old case.

00:05:58.079 --> 00:05:59.040
I cannot thank you enough.

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:04.920
By the way...

00:06:05.399 --> 00:06:06.040
...what about Chao Yun?

00:06:10.319 --> 00:06:10.920
What about her?

00:06:11.680 --> 00:06:12.319
Let's go take a look.

00:06:12.800 --> 00:06:13.399
All right.

00:06:13.759 --> 00:06:14.279
Let's go.

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:27.319
A Liang?

00:06:27.879 --> 00:06:28.680
What happened?

00:06:37.839 --> 00:06:38.360
Who's there?

00:06:44.360 --> 00:06:45.000
Come out!

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:48.279
That...

00:06:50.199 --> 00:06:51.759
...that is the Madam's portrait.

00:07:13.439 --> 00:07:14.720
It seems the missing heads

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:16.360
are all here.

00:07:20.079 --> 00:07:21.879
Who put their heads here?

00:07:23.439 --> 00:07:24.160
More importantly,

00:07:24.959 --> 00:07:26.879
I want to know who these empty spirit tablets

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:28.480
are reserved for.

00:07:31.759 --> 00:07:32.639
Could it be that

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:34.199
next,

00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:36.240
five more people will die?

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:42.480
No intention to disturb.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:45.720
Amitabha.

00:07:47.240 --> 00:07:48.839
Xu Guangqu.

00:07:50.879 --> 00:07:51.839
No intention to disturb you all.

00:07:51.839 --> 00:07:52.920
That is the Manor Lord's name.

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:53.720
Yes.

00:07:54.360 --> 00:07:56.079
The Lord's surname wasn't originally Xu.

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:59.079
He took the Lady's surname after marrying into the Manor.

00:08:02.279 --> 00:08:04.000
This looks like an altar.

00:08:04.839 --> 00:08:05.720
To mourn the Lady.

00:08:08.399 --> 00:08:09.519
Did these people

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:10.920
have any grievances with the Lady?

00:08:12.600 --> 00:08:13.680
I'm not sure.

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:17.560
Did the Lady have close friends or loyal servants?

00:08:19.279 --> 00:08:21.759
The Lady always looked after the Young Master.

00:08:21.759 --> 00:08:23.000
She rarely interacted with the outside world.

00:08:24.279 --> 00:08:25.560
After the Lady passed away,

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:27.680
the Lord dismissed all the servants

00:08:27.839 --> 00:08:29.079
who had served her.

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:38.600
Why are you carrying flower petals?

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:43.960
I don't really like scent pouches,

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:46.000
so I carry some petals.

00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:08.440
What's that noise?

00:09:08.799 --> 00:09:09.399
Don't be afraid.

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:11.279
They must have found the secret passage.

00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:13.200
How did they find it?

00:09:15.039 --> 00:09:15.720
What is that?

00:09:15.879 --> 00:09:16.320
Give it to me.

00:09:16.919 --> 00:09:17.600
It's nothing.

00:09:17.919 --> 00:09:18.799
Those are flower petals inside.

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:22.200
So it was you.

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:27.519
You...

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:28.759
I'm sorry, Master Ye.

00:09:28.960 --> 00:09:30.240
I didn't want to betray you.

00:09:30.559 --> 00:09:32.440
But they simply offered too much.

00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:35.080
They are all inside.

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:36.679
The Thousand-Mechanism Treasure is also inside.

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:38.480
But this isn't what we were told.

00:09:38.600 --> 00:09:39.519
There's no treasure in here.

00:09:46.519 --> 00:09:47.360
Capture Ye Li alive.

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:48.000
Yes!

00:09:56.720 --> 00:09:57.200
Hurry up!

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.120
What's wrong?

00:10:11.320 --> 00:10:12.240
I need to relieve myself.

00:10:12.360 --> 00:10:12.919
Hold it.

00:10:14.600 --> 00:10:15.159
Fine.

00:10:16.039 --> 00:10:17.399
Then I'll just do it right here.

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:31.120
Who is it?

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:32.639
It's me.

00:10:34.200 --> 00:10:35.120
Why are you here?

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:38.320
Are Master Ye and Xiao Bai alright?

00:10:39.039 --> 00:10:40.039
They are safe for now.

00:10:40.519 --> 00:10:41.480
You have to do me a favor.

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:45.639
If it is within my power,

00:10:45.919 --> 00:10:46.720
I will do my best.

00:10:56.559 --> 00:10:57.360
Eunuch Liu.

00:10:58.039 --> 00:10:58.960
Going back on your word

00:10:59.240 --> 00:11:00.360
is not the conduct of a gentleman.

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:02.320
Gentleman?

00:11:07.279 --> 00:11:09.279
I'm not even a man,

00:11:09.639 --> 00:11:11.480
let alone a gentleman.

00:11:11.840 --> 00:11:13.559
I am the Chief of the Grand Court.

00:11:14.200 --> 00:11:16.159
Do you have evidence to detain me, Eunuch Liu?

00:11:18.039 --> 00:11:19.159
Evidence?

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:23.320
It is written clearly right here.

00:11:24.440 --> 00:11:25.679
Who would have thought

00:11:25.679 --> 00:11:29.000
His Highness the Crown Prince and the Manor Lord

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:30.919
would commit such dirty deeds,

00:11:31.960 --> 00:11:35.000
implicating even the Chief of the Grand Court.

00:11:35.639 --> 00:11:36.279
Isn't that right?

00:11:36.759 --> 00:11:37.559
Let go of me!

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:38.759
Let go!

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:46.399
Eunuch.

00:11:47.039 --> 00:11:49.320
Si Niang was sneaking around in the corner just now.

00:11:49.840 --> 00:11:50.639
I found her suspicious,

00:11:51.159 --> 00:11:52.120
so I tied her up and brought her here.

00:11:59.240 --> 00:12:00.080
What?

00:12:01.039 --> 00:12:02.039
Trying to run?

00:12:05.960 --> 00:12:07.080
Of course I am.

00:12:08.120 --> 00:12:09.639
Rather than waiting here to die,

00:12:10.200 --> 00:12:12.080
I'd rather run out and try my luck.

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:14.240
What if I actually escape?

00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:21.519
No wonder a brothel woman like you

00:12:21.759 --> 00:12:24.120
caught the eye of the Manor Lord.

00:12:24.919 --> 00:12:26.080
Interesting.

00:12:27.200 --> 00:12:28.039
Men!

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:30.240
Cut out her tongue

00:12:30.399 --> 00:12:31.960
and break her legs.

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:34.159
I'll put an end to your hopes.

00:12:34.159 --> 00:12:34.679
You wouldn't dare!

00:12:37.279 --> 00:12:38.320
She is my lover!

00:12:39.159 --> 00:12:40.399
If she loses a single hair,

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:42.799
you won't leave here alive!

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:47.480
When did this happen?

00:12:48.519 --> 00:12:49.840
Does the Metropolitan Governor know?

00:12:50.120 --> 00:12:51.000
Cut the crap.

00:12:51.679 --> 00:12:52.480
If you have the guts,

00:12:52.960 --> 00:12:53.600
come at me!

00:12:53.799 --> 00:12:55.159
Then I will grant your wish.

00:12:55.600 --> 00:12:56.200
Men!

00:12:56.759 --> 00:12:58.399
Give him fifty strokes of the cane first.

00:13:08.519 --> 00:13:09.480
Let go!

00:13:15.799 --> 00:13:16.919
Let go!

00:13:19.159 --> 00:13:19.720
Eunuch Liu!

00:13:20.559 --> 00:13:22.159
Is this how you ask for a favor?

00:13:25.879 --> 00:13:28.240
Find the murderer who killed Huang Cui.

00:13:28.720 --> 00:13:30.039
I want them alive.

00:13:30.360 --> 00:13:31.000
Fine.

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:32.759
However...

00:13:38.600 --> 00:13:39.840
Stop for now.

00:13:49.600 --> 00:13:50.279
Speak.

00:13:50.919 --> 00:13:52.240
Who is the murderer?

00:14:03.960 --> 00:14:05.159
I am the murderer.